 horsey set sports illustrated december   retrieved december    a b c phelps media group and united states equestrian team foundation uset foundation president emeritus finn mw caspersen – media release september   retrieved november    stevenson alexandra goldstein matthew march   private equity executive accused of faking investments new york times retrieved march     kwoh leslie finn caspersen funeral draws hundreds of family friends in morristown the starledger september   retrieved october    jaffer nancy finn caspersen american combined driving advocate dies equisearch september   retrieved october    mascarenhas rohan former nj power broker philanthropist finn caspersen dies in apparent suicide the starledger september   retrieved december    a b garreau joel edge city life on the new frontier new york random house  –  a b caspersen center dedication raises olympic flag as officially designated olympic training site rowk december   retrieved october    princeton national rowing association finn m w caspersen rowing center boathouse retrieved october    a b staff closing a conversation with finn caspersen ’ harvard law bulletin fall  retrieved november    platts james t law school receives  million donation the harvard crimson september   retrieved november    jiang athena y harvard law school raises  million in capital campaign the harvard crimson october   retrieved november    hsu nelson c room in law library named after caspersen the harvard crimson october   retrieved november    harvard law school – facilities management wasserstein hall caspersen student center clinical wing – about the building retrieved october    law school dedicates new building complex aimed at improving student experience harvard gazette april   retrieved january    the scrapbook prize duds the weekly standard  april   retrieved december    oconnell kaete stepping down caspersen will end year reign as chair the acorn drew university campus newspaper october   text after serving as