asked to “check on” him casperson came from a wealthy family and moved with powerful people and he was known for his political influence fundraising and philanthropy family members including his son bedminster township committeeman finn mw caspersen jr declined to comment on the death of casperson sr or the circumstances surrounding his demise in addition to philanthropic ventures casperson was an accomplished equestrian and fellow movers and shakers have commented to press on his legacy “finn was always a gentleman and always made his resources available” said rhode island state senator dennis algiere who represents the seaside region just across the state line from connecticut “he was a very charitable individual he donated a lot of time and money to various organizations in our community over the years” “i don’t think you could find someone more philanthropic or caring” said tucker johnson an equestrian and a friend of caspersen’s according to a statement on an equestrian web site source bloomberg now read this reinforcing china’s borders and ‘the great illusion’ opinion share  tweet  share  share  pin it  contributor kim lacapria tags finn casperson finn hw casperson financial meltdown deaths july   ‘star wars episode ’ rumor podracing to return july   ‘star wars episode ’ rumor benicio del toro’s character is from ‘bloodline’ novel comments latest headlines update on rumors of ‘wreckit ralph’ attraction replacing stitch’s great escape in magic kingdom ‘big brother ’ recap spoilers from july  episode include who went home tonight who is the new hoh jill duggar dillard dubbed ‘most affectionate with spouse’ by siblings kristy manzanares facebook photos videos kenneth manzanares said wife  ‘would not stop laughing at me’ ‘dance moms’ season  chloe lukasiak unsure to join former aldc members again too busy for lifetime show search continues for missing detroit teen jaylon wilson  who was last seen being tossed in trunk of car ‘days of our lives’ spoilers nicole to 